### Add Delivery Address
POST {{host}}/api/user/delivery-addresses
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "name": "Home",
  "fullName": "John Doe",
  "street": "123 Main St",
  "city": "New York",
  "postalCode": "10001",
  "country": "US",
  "phoneNumber": "+1234567890",
  "isDefault": true
}

### Expected Response (Success - 201 Created):
# The `active` field indicates whether the address matches the user's current country of residence.
# Content-Type: application/json
#
# {
#   "id": "0192e4a0-7b3a-7f00-8000-000000000001",
#   "name": "Home",
#   "fullName": "John Doe",
#   "street": "123 Main St",
#   "city": "New York",
#   "postalCode": "10001",
#   "country": "US",
#   "phoneNumber": "+1234567890",
#   "isDefault": true,
#   "active": true
# }

### Get Delivery Addresses
# Returns all delivery addresses for the authenticated user.
# Each address includes an `active` flag indicating whether it matches the user's current country of residence.
# Only active addresses can be used for purchases.
GET {{host}}/api/user/delivery-addresses/
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Expected Response (Success - 200 OK):
# Content-Type: application/json
#
# [
#   {
#     "id": "0192e4a0-7b3a-7f00-8000-000000000001",
#     "name": "Home",
#     "fullName": "John Doe",
#     "street": "123 Main St",
#     "city": "New York",
#     "postalCode": "10001",
#     "country": "US",
#     "phoneNumber": "+1234567890",
#     "isDefault": true,
#     "active": true
#   },
#   {
#     "id": "0192e4a0-7b3a-7f00-8000-000000000002",
#     "name": "Poland Home",
#     "fullName": "Jan Kowalski",
#     "street": "ul. Marszałkowska 1",
#     "city": "Warsaw",
#     "postalCode": "00-001",
#     "country": "PL",
#     "phoneNumber": "+48123456789",
#     "isDefault": false,
#     "active": false
#   }
# ]

### Get User Preferences
GET {{host}}/api/user/preferences
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Accept-Language: pl-PL

### Update User Preferences
PUT {{host}}/api/user/preferences
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "language": "pl-PL",
  "preferredCurrency": "PLN",
  "countryOfResidence": "PL"
}

### Partially Update User Preferences
PATCH {{host}}/api/user/preferences
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "preferredCurrency": "ARRR"
}

### Partially Update User Preferences - Set Country of Residence
PATCH {{host}}/api/user/preferences
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "countryOfResidence": "US"
}
